commit.message:
Create starcitizen.rules 

adds rule for starcitizen
Ignore os.realpath exception for TPid creation

Apply rules only once on new found processes

Keep a state for each TPID of rules that have
already been apllied, this means that we don't have to
re-check current value for each process.

Also update global proc dict, with new and exited processes, so
we can keep track of each process state.

Add clang-tidy

Clang-tidy is a static analyser and as such is very CPU and IO intensive. Make it ``BG_CPUIO`` like we do with compilers.

Updated README.md

Corrected some grammar errors
Rules for DisplayLink dock driver added

Change teams from Realtime RT to Chat.

Teams is a chat app, lowlatency RT doesn't really fit.
